{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":817,"text":"Think of a hard choice\nyou'll face in the near future."},{"time":4391,"text":"It might be between two careers --"},{"time":6236,"text":"artist and accountant --"},{"time":8286,"text":"or places to live --\nthe city or the country --"},{"time":11123,"text":"or even between two people to marry --"},{"time":13021,"text":"you could marry Betty\nor you could marry Lolita."},{"time":16572,"text":"Or it might be a choice\nabout whether to have children,"},{"time":19589,"text":"to have an ailing parent move in with you,"},{"time":21960,"text":"to raise your child in a religion\nthat your partner lives by"},{"time":25201,"text":"but leaves you cold."},{"time":27236,"text":"Or whether to donate\nyour life savings to charity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30622,"text":"Chances are, the hard choice\nyou thought of was something big,"},{"time":33560,"text":"something momentous,\nsomething that matters to you."},{"time":36763,"text":"Hard choices seem to be occasions"},{"time":39053,"text":"for agonizing, hand-wringing,\nthe gnashing of teeth."},{"time":44073,"text":"But I think we've\nmisunderstood hard choices"},{"time":46162,"text":"and the role they play in our lives."},{"time":48253,"text":"Understanding hard choices"},{"time":50155,"text":"uncovers a hidden power\neach of us possesses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54972,"text":"What makes a choice hard\nis the way the alternatives relate."},{"time":58909,"text":"In any easy choice,"},{"time":60383,"text":"one alternative is better than the other."},{"time":62910,"text":"In a hard choice,"},{"time":64403,"text":"one alternative is better in some ways,"},{"time":66955,"text":"the other alternative\nis better in other ways,"},{"time":69180,"text":"and neither is better\nthan the other overall."},{"time":72732,"text":"You agonize over whether to stay\nin your current job in the city"},{"time":77003,"text":"or uproot your life\nfor more challenging work in the country,"},{"time":81479,"text":"because staying is better in some ways,"},{"time":83705,"text":"moving is better in others,"},{"time":85329,"text":"and neither is better\nthan the other overall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89368,"text":"We shouldn't think\nthat all hard choices are big."},{"time":93023,"text":"Let's say you're deciding\nwhat to have for breakfast."},{"time":95654,"text":"You could have high fiber bran cereal"},{"time":98534,"text":"or a chocolate donut."},{"time":100199,"text":"Suppose what matters in the choice\nis tastiness and healthfulness."},{"time":104563,"text":"The cereal is better for you,"},{"time":106829,"text":"the donut tastes way better,"},{"time":109010,"text":"but neither is better\nthan the other overall,"},{"time":111236,"text":"a hard choice."},{"time":113348,"text":"Realizing that small choices\ncan also be hard,"},{"time":117372,"text":"may make big hard choices\nseem less intractable."},{"time":121563,"text":"After all, we manage to figure out\nwhat to have for breakfast,"},{"time":124493,"text":"so maybe we can figure out\nwhether to stay in the city"},{"time":127648,"text":"or uproot for the new job in the country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131789,"text":"We also shouldn't think\nthat hard choices are hard"},{"time":136365,"text":"because we are stupid."},{"time":138692,"text":"When I graduated from college,"},{"time":140632,"text":"I couldn't decide between two careers,\nphilosophy and law."},{"time":144158,"text":"I really loved philosophy."},{"time":147600,"text":"There are amazing things\nyou can learn as a philosopher,"},{"time":150576,"text":"and all from the comfort of an armchair."},{"time":154106,"text":"But I came from a modest immigrant family"},{"time":157008,"text":"where my idea of luxury"},{"time":158481,"text":"was having a pork tongue\nand jelly sandwich"},{"time":160990,"text":"in my school lunchbox,"},{"time":163232,"text":"so the thought of spending my whole life"},{"time":165621,"text":"sitting around in armchairs\njust thinking ..."},{"time":169335,"text":"Well, that struck me as the height\nof extravagance and frivolity."},{"time":173357,"text":"So I got out my yellow pad,"},{"time":175127,"text":"I drew a line down the middle,"},{"time":177034,"text":"and I tried my best\nto think of the reasons"},{"time":179455,"text":"for and against each alternative."},{"time":183199,"text":"I remember thinking to myself,"},{"time":185413,"text":"if only I knew what my life\nin each career would be like."},{"time":190428,"text":"If only God or Netflix would send me a DVD\nof my two possible future careers,"},{"time":196439,"text":"I'd be set."},{"time":197635,"text":"I'd compare them side by side,"},{"time":199561,"text":"I'd see that one was better,"},{"time":201492,"text":"and the choice would be easy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203867,"text":"But I got no DVD,"},{"time":205976,"text":"and because I couldn't\nfigure out which was better,"},{"time":208843,"text":"I did what many of us do in hard choices:"},{"time":211580,"text":"I took the safest option."},{"time":214466,"text":"Fear of being an unemployed philosopher\nled me to become a lawyer,"},{"time":220256,"text":"and as I discovered,\nlawyering didn't quite fit."},{"time":223610,"text":"It wasn't who I was."},{"time":225889,"text":"So now I'm a philosopher,"},{"time":227527,"text":"and I study hard choices,"},{"time":229489,"text":"and I can tell you,\nthat fear of the unknown,"},{"time":232838,"text":"while a common motivational default\nin dealing with hard choices,"},{"time":237958,"text":"rests on a misconception of them."},{"time":240505,"text":"It's a mistake to think\nthat in hard choices,"},{"time":243459,"text":"one alternative\nreally is better than the other,"},{"time":246477,"text":"but we're too stupid to know which,"},{"time":248460,"text":"and since we don't know which,"},{"time":249927,"text":"we might as well take\nthe least risky option."},{"time":252825,"text":"Even taking two alternatives side by side"},{"time":255207,"text":"with full information,\na choice can still be hard."},{"time":260099,"text":"Hard choices are hard\nnot because of us or our ignorance;"},{"time":264179,"text":"they're hard because there\nis no best option."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269231,"text":"Now, if there's no best option,"},{"time":271179,"text":"if the scales don't tip in favor\nof one alternative over another,"},{"time":276060,"text":"then surely the alternatives\nmust be equally good."},{"time":279797,"text":"So maybe the right thing\nto say in hard choices"},{"time":282092,"text":"is that they're\nbetween equally good options."},{"time":284770,"text":"But that can't be right."},{"time":285955,"text":"If alternatives are equally good,\nyou should just flip a coin between them,"},{"time":289898,"text":"and it seems a mistake to think,"},{"time":292333,"text":"here's how you should\ndecide between careers,"},{"time":294907,"text":"places to live, people to marry:"},{"time":296501,"text":"Flip a coin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299156,"text":"There's another reason for thinking"},{"time":300891,"text":"that hard choices aren't choices\nbetween equally good options."},{"time":306063,"text":"Suppose you have a choice\nbetween two jobs:"},{"time":309744,"text":"you could be an investment banker"},{"time":312708,"text":"or a graphic artist."},{"time":315220,"text":"There are a variety of things\nthat matter in such a choice,"},{"time":318036,"text":"like the excitement of the work,"},{"time":320615,"text":"achieving financial security,"},{"time":322376,"text":"having time to raise a family, and so on."},{"time":324750,"text":"Maybe the artist's career\nputs you on the cutting edge"},{"time":329209,"text":"of new forms of pictorial expression."},{"time":332049,"text":"Maybe the banking career\nputs you on the cutting edge"},{"time":334869,"text":"of new forms of financial manipulation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338012,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339620,"text":"Imagine the two jobs however you like,"},{"time":342584,"text":"so that neither is better than the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345696,"text":"Now suppose we improve one of them, a bit."},{"time":348673,"text":"Suppose the bank, wooing you,"},{"time":351612,"text":"adds 500 dollars a month to your salary."},{"time":354432,"text":"Does the extra money"},{"time":355806,"text":"now make the banking job\nbetter than the artist one?"},{"time":360940,"text":"Not necessarily."},{"time":363049,"text":"A higher salary makes the banking job\nbetter than it was before,"},{"time":367180,"text":"but it might not be enough"},{"time":368822,"text":"to make being a banker\nbetter than being an artist."},{"time":373299,"text":"But if an improvement in one of the jobs\ndoesn't make it better than the other,"},{"time":377790,"text":"then the two original jobs\ncould not have been equally good."},{"time":381812,"text":"If you start with two things\nthat are equally good,"},{"time":384233,"text":"and you improve one of them,"},{"time":385598,"text":"it now must be better than the other."},{"time":388653,"text":"That's not the case\nwith options in hard choices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393393,"text":"So now we've got a puzzle."},{"time":395755,"text":"We've got two jobs."},{"time":397387,"text":"Neither is better than the other,\nnor are they equally good."},{"time":401526,"text":"So how are we supposed to choose?"},{"time":403955,"text":"Something seems to have gone wrong here."},{"time":408303,"text":"Maybe the choice itself is problematic,\nand comparison is impossible."},{"time":414184,"text":"But that can't be right."},{"time":415748,"text":"It's not like we're trying to choose\nbetween two things that can't be compared."},{"time":420234,"text":"We're weighing the merits\nof two jobs, after all,"},{"time":423135,"text":"not the merits of the number nine\nand a plate of fried eggs."},{"time":428052,"text":"A comparison of the overall\nmerits of two jobs"},{"time":431420,"text":"is something we can make,"},{"time":433331,"text":"and one we often do make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437407,"text":"I think the puzzle arises"},{"time":439487,"text":"because of an unreflective assumption\nwe make about value."},{"time":443995,"text":"We unwittingly assume that values\nlike justice, beauty, kindness,"},{"time":450006,"text":"are akin to scientific quantities,\nlike length, mass and weight."},{"time":457247,"text":"Take any comparative question\nnot involving value,"},{"time":460362,"text":"such as which of two suitcases is heavier."},{"time":463907,"text":"There are only three possibilities."},{"time":466648,"text":"The weight of one is greater, lesser\nor equal to the weight of the other."},{"time":472605,"text":"Properties like weight can be\nrepresented by real numbers --"},{"time":475803,"text":"one, two, three and so on --"},{"time":477765,"text":"and there are only\nthree possible comparisons"},{"time":480847,"text":"between any two real numbers."},{"time":483240,"text":"One number is greater, lesser,\nor equal to the other."},{"time":488475,"text":"Not so with values."},{"time":491440,"text":"As post-Enlightenment creatures,"},{"time":493291,"text":"we tend to assume"},{"time":495265,"text":"that scientific thinking holds the key\nto everything of importance in our world,"},{"time":501050,"text":"but the world of value\nis different from the world of science."},{"time":504640,"text":"The stuff of the one world\ncan be quantified by real numbers."},{"time":508252,"text":"The stuff of the other world can't."},{"time":511712,"text":"We shouldn't assume that the world of is,\nof lengths and weights,"},{"time":516008,"text":"has the same structure\nas the world of ought,"},{"time":518939,"text":"of what we should do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520904,"text":"So if what matters to us --"},{"time":523009,"text":"a child's delight, the love\nyou have for your partner —"},{"time":526547,"text":"can't be represented by real numbers,"},{"time":529375,"text":"then there's no reason to believe"},{"time":531341,"text":"that in choice, there are only\nthree possibilities --"},{"time":535181,"text":"that one alternative is better,\nworse or equal to the other."},{"time":540464,"text":"We need to introduce\na new, fourth relation"},{"time":544730,"text":"beyond being better, worse or equal,"},{"time":548369,"text":"that describes what's going on\nin hard choices."},{"time":551960,"text":"I like to say that\nthe alternatives are \"on a par.\""},{"time":555151,"text":"When alternatives are on a par,"},{"time":557075,"text":"it may matter very much which you choose,"},{"time":560465,"text":"but one alternative\nisn't better than the other."},{"time":563404,"text":"Rather, the alternatives are\nin the same neighborhood of value,"},{"time":567806,"text":"in the same league of value,"},{"time":569877,"text":"while at the same time\nbeing very different in kind of value."},{"time":574444,"text":"That's why the choice is hard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577754,"text":"Understanding hard choices in this way"},{"time":580187,"text":"uncovers something\nabout ourselves we didn't know."},{"time":584266,"text":"Each of us has the power\nto create reasons."},{"time":590172,"text":"Imagine a world\nin which every choice you face"},{"time":593510,"text":"is an easy choice,"},{"time":594907,"text":"that is, there's always\na best alternative."},{"time":597207,"text":"If there's a best alternative,\nthen that's the one you should choose,"},{"time":600614,"text":"because part of being rational"},{"time":602400,"text":"is doing the better thing\nrather than the worse thing,"},{"time":605139,"text":"choosing what you have\nmost reason to choose."},{"time":608567,"text":"In such a world,"},{"time":610297,"text":"we'd have most reason"},{"time":612722,"text":"to wear black socks instead of pink socks,"},{"time":615193,"text":"to eat cereal instead of donuts,"},{"time":617153,"text":"to live in the city\nrather than the country,"},{"time":619231,"text":"to marry Betty instead of Lolita."},{"time":621126,"text":"A world full of only easy choices\nwould enslave us to reasons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627963,"text":"When you think about it,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":629290,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":630504,"text":"it's nuts to believe\nthat the reasons given to you"},{"time":636235,"text":"dictated that you had\nmost reason to pursue"},{"time":641006,"text":"the exact hobbies you do,"},{"time":643952,"text":"to live in the exact house you do,"},{"time":646173,"text":"to work at the exact job you do."},{"time":649471,"text":"Instead, you faced alternatives\nthat were on a par --"},{"time":653959,"text":"hard choices --"},{"time":655149,"text":"and you made reasons for yourself"},{"time":658186,"text":"to choose that hobby,\nthat house and that job."},{"time":663004,"text":"When alternatives are on a par,"},{"time":665261,"text":"the reasons given to us,"},{"time":666813,"text":"the ones that determine\nwhether we're making a mistake,"},{"time":669793,"text":"are silent as to what to do."},{"time":672989,"text":"It's here, in the space of hard choices,"},{"time":676702,"text":"that we get to exercise\nour normative power --"},{"time":681280,"text":"the power to create reasons for yourself,"},{"time":683816,"text":"to make yourself into the kind of person"},{"time":688226,"text":"for whom country living\nis preferable to the urban life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693337,"text":"When we choose between options\nthat are on a par,"},{"time":696743,"text":"we can do something\nreally rather remarkable."},{"time":700495,"text":"We can put our very selves\nbehind an option."},{"time":704325,"text":"Here's where I stand."},{"time":706910,"text":"Here's who I am, I am for banking."},{"time":710132,"text":"I am for chocolate donuts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712291,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714370,"text":"This response in hard choices\nis a rational response,"},{"time":718721,"text":"but it's not dictated\nby reasons given to us."},{"time":721421,"text":"Rather, it's supported\nby reasons created by us."},{"time":727765,"text":"When we create reasons for ourselves"},{"time":730356,"text":"to become this kind\nof person rather than that,"},{"time":733646,"text":"we wholeheartedly become\nthe people that we are."},{"time":737620,"text":"You might say that we become\nthe authors of our own lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743047,"text":"So when we face hard choices,\nwe shouldn't beat our head against a wall"},{"time":747668,"text":"trying to figure out\nwhich alternative is better."},{"time":750045,"text":"There is no best alternative."},{"time":752502,"text":"Instead of looking for reasons out there,"},{"time":755062,"text":"we should be looking for reasons in here:"},{"time":757823,"text":"Who am I to be?"},{"time":760278,"text":"You might decide to be\na pink sock-wearing,"},{"time":763744,"text":"cereal-loving, country-living banker,"},{"time":767657,"text":"and I might decide to be\na black sock-wearing,"},{"time":770873,"text":"urban, donut-loving artist."},{"time":774132,"text":"What we do in hard choices\nis very much up to each of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780887,"text":"Now, people who don't exercise\ntheir normative powers in hard choices"},{"time":785736,"text":"are drifters."},{"time":787513,"text":"We all know people like that."},{"time":789125,"text":"I drifted into being a lawyer."},{"time":791445,"text":"I didn't put my agency behind lawyering."},{"time":793603,"text":"I wasn't for lawyering."},{"time":796542,"text":"Drifters allow the world\nto write the story of their lives."},{"time":801439,"text":"They let mechanisms\nof reward and punishment --"},{"time":805291,"text":"pats on the head, fear,\nthe easiness of an option --"},{"time":809230,"text":"to determine what they do."},{"time":811936,"text":"So the lesson of hard choices:"},{"time":814373,"text":"reflect on what you can\nput your agency behind,"},{"time":818861,"text":"on what you can be for,"},{"time":821530,"text":"and through hard choices,"},{"time":823769,"text":"become that person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827199,"text":"Far from being sources of agony and dread,"},{"time":830056,"text":"hard choices are precious opportunities"},{"time":833432,"text":"for us to celebrate what is special\nabout the human condition,"},{"time":837370,"text":"that the reasons that govern\nour choices as correct or incorrect"},{"time":841997,"text":"sometimes run out,"},{"time":843687,"text":"and it is here, in the space\nof hard choices,"},{"time":846786,"text":"that we have the power\nto create reasons for ourselves"},{"time":850927,"text":"to become the distinctive\npeople that we are."},{"time":854496,"text":"And that's why hard\nchoices are not a curse"},{"time":857246,"text":"but a godsend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":858967,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":860162,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}